query:
UPDATE v2_queue
                            SET flow_status = JSONB_SET(flow_status, ARRAY['modules', $1::TEXT, 'branchall', 'branch'], ((flow_status->'modules'->$1::int->'branchall'->>'branch')::int + 1)::text::jsonb),
                            last_ping = NULL
                            WHERE id = $2
                            RETURNING (flow_status->'modules'->$1::int->'branchall'->>'branch')::int
